00:43:39.679 --> 00:43:40.519
Why?

00:43:40.519 --> 00:43:42.799
Because we don't wanna have that tragic result.

00:43:42.799 --> 00:43:45.399
We don't wanna limit God.

00:43:45.399 --> 00:43:46.239
Let's pray.

00:43:46.239 --> 00:43:47.079
Father, we love you.

00:43:47.079 --> 00:43:48.159
Thank you for loving us.

00:43:48.159 --> 00:43:50.439
Thank you for your word, the truth contained therein.

00:43:50.439 --> 00:43:54.919
Thank you for giving us what we need.

00:43:54.919 --> 00:43:56.439
And I pray that you'd help us, Lord,

00:43:56.439 --> 00:43:58.359
to have our faith increase.

00:43:58.359 --> 00:44:00.759
Lord, help us to examine our hearts.

00:44:00.759 --> 00:44:04.859
Lord, if there's any area of unbelief in our lives,

00:44:04.859 --> 00:44:06.959
Lord, would you help us to deal with that?

00:44:07.959 --> 00:44:09.759
God, I don't wanna limit you.

00:44:11.039 --> 00:44:14.079
In my life, in our church,

00:44:16.239 --> 00:44:17.799
help us to have faith.

00:44:17.799 --> 00:44:19.839
Help us to believe you.

00:44:19.839 --> 00:44:20.919
Bless the time of prayer.

00:44:20.919 --> 00:44:22.199
Thank you for the privilege.

00:44:22.199 --> 00:44:23.519
I pray that you'd be honored and glorified

00:44:23.519 --> 00:44:26.799
for it's in Christ's name we pray, amen.

